title: Shares of several technology companies are trading lower amid market weakness, selling off from recent sector strength. Equities have moved lower for the session following US unemployment data and recent cautious comments from the WHO. Sentiment is also negative following cautious comments from Fed Chair Powell and bearish outlook from some major US investors on Wednesday.
